1 (d) (c) A county election board has exclusive jurisdiction to disband
2 any of the following:
3 (1) A candidate's committee for a local office.
4 (2) A candidate's committee for a school board office.
5 (3) A political action committee that has filed a statement or
6 report with the election board, unless the political action
